{"id":10256,"date":"2021-03-23T02:40:12","date_gmt":"2021-03-23T02:40:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=10256"},"modified":"2021-03-23T07:01:25","modified_gmt":"2021-03-23T07:01:25","slug":"noi-that-byzan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/noi-that-byzan\/","title":{"rendered":"N\u1ed8I TH\u1ea4T BYZAN THI\u1ebeT K\u1ebe THI C\u00d4NG N\u1ed8I TH\u1ea4T TR\u1eccN G\u00d3I"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan<\/strong><\/a> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 uy t\u00edn, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. V\u1edbi h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng, Byzan \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u00f9ng c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng ti\u1ec7n nghi.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"614\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/10-1-1024x614.jpg\" alt=\"noi-that-byzan-thiet-ke-thi-cong-noi-that-tron-goi\" class=\"wp-image-10257\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/10-1-1024x614.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/10-1-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/10-1-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/10-1-1536x921.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/10-1.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Byzan &#8211; \u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m trong ngh\u1ec1, Byzan hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng, m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng ho\u00e0n m\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 hay c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng ti\u1ec7n nghi, m\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t theo th\u1eddi gian. T\u1ea1i Byzan ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng quy tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eb1m mang t\u1edbi cho kh\u00e1ch c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn t\u1ed5ng qu\u00e1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u201c<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/noi-that-tron-goi\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/noi-that-tron-goi\/\">n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i<\/a><\/strong>\u201d.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/2-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"noi-that-byzan-thiet-ke-thi-cong-noi-that-tron-goi\" class=\"wp-image-10258\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/2-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/2-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/2-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/2-1.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong h\u1eb1ng h\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7n nay. B\u1edfi Byzan kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t t\u1ed1i \u01b0u, h\u01a1n h\u1ebft ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t, bao g\u1ed3m:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t&nbsp;<\/li><li>S\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t&nbsp;<\/li><li>Thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i, c\u00e1c Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 Byzan lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin, thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u01b0 duy, m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ec3 hai ch\u1eef Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i trong m\u1ed7i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-2 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"724\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/0001-2-1024x724.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"10260\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/0001-2-scaled.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/?attachment_id=10260\" class=\"wp-image-10260\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/0001-2-1024x724.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/0001-2-300x212.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/0001-2-768x543.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/0001-2-1536x1086.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/000