y khoan cam, m\u00e1y d\u00e1n c\u1ea1nh,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88751-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10261\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88751-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88751-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88751-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88751-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88751-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88751-scaled.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88391-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10262\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88391-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88391-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88391-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88391-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88391-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/IMG_88391-scaled.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m trong ngh\u1ec1, l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn, \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5ng quan nh\u1ea5t. Hi\u1ec7n nay, N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan \u0111ang h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb cung \u1ee9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t uy t\u00edn tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Do \u0111\u00f3, khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn cho t\u1ed5 \u1ea5m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed aligncenter is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i - Sang tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 cao c\u1ea5p 100m2 Vinhomes West Point | Byzan Interior\" width=\"1020\" height=\"574\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/2MLKOv7el70?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Byzan &#8211; Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i&nbsp;<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111a phong c\u00e1ch, Byzan ch\u1ec9 chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u 1 ph\u00f2ng c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn r\u1ed9ng c\u00f9ng t\u01b0 duy s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, \u1edf m\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng Byzan \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, gu th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"569\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/810c3a2308a1fbffa2b021-2-1024x569.jpg\" alt=\"noi-that-byzan-thiet-ke-thi-cong-noi-that-tron-goi\" class=\"wp-image-10265\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/810c3a2308a1fbffa2b021-2-1024x569.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/810c3a2308a1fbffa2b021-2-300x167.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/810c3a2308a1fbffa2b021-2-768x427.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/810c3a2308a1fbffa2b021-2-1536x853.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/810c3a2308a1fbffa2b021-2-140x79.jpg 140w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/810c3a2308a1fbffa2b021-2.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>L\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, d\u00e1m b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, Ki\u1ebfn Tr\u00fac S\u01b0 Byzan lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t mong mu\u1ed1n, nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u. T\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u1eebng phi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e1, vi\u00ean g\u1ea1ch, t\u1ea5m g\u1ed7,&#8230; t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh to\u00e1n k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea3nh quan c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh. B\u1edfi h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t, h\u00e0i h\u00f2a trong s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t di\u1ec7u.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Byzan Design<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Byzan cam k\u1ebft lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch trong t\u1eebng giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 nh\u1eb1m mang t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng d\u00f9 10 n\u0103m n\u1eefa v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Byzan l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ty thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u00f3 showroom s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Byzan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn tr\u1ef1c quan nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp b\u00e0y tr\u00ed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>2. Byzan l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ti\u00ean phong t\u1ea1o ra xu h\u01b0\u1edbng trong phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 m\u1ea3ng kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/7c56f395c61735496c0632-1-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10264\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/7c56f395c61735496c0632-1-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/7c56f395c61735496c0632-1-300x188.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/7c56f395c61735496c0632-1-768x480.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/7c56f395c61735496c0632-1-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/7c56f395c61735496c0632-1.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>3. Kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda t\u1edbi khi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>4. Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb h\u01a1n #10% so th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap Byzan t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, m\u00e1y m\u00f3c v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c d\u01b0\u1edbi quy tr\u00ecnh nghi\u00eam ng\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ho\u00e1 cao.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>5. D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 10 n\u0103m, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 sau b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i mang l\u1ea1i cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 an t\u00e2m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u00f9ng quy tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c minh b\u1ea1ch, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp, N\u1ed9i Th\u1ea5t Byzan \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u uy t\u00edn v\u00e0 tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c hi\u1ec7n nay. N\u1ebfu qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ea7n t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i nh\u00e0 nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1, bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 v\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 t\u1edbi s\u1ed1 <strong>Hotline\/ Zalo 0932.262.123<\/strong> \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>>> <strong>Xem th\u00eam: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/noi-that-can-ho-dle-roi-soleil-xuan-dieu\/\" target=\"_blank\">Thi\u1ebft K\u1ebf N\u1ed9i Th\u1ea5t C\u0103n H\u1ed9 D\u2019le Roi Soleil Xu\u00e2n Di\u1ec7u<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>>> <strong>Xem th\u00eam: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/noi-that-chung-cu-royal-city\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/noi-that-chung-cu-royal-city\/\" target=\"_blank\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u0103n h\